            <abstract>
                <p>Sǝbḥata fǝqur-hymn to St George of Lydda.
                  The manuscript tradition seems to differ in varying degrees from the printed edition.
                In some of the modern editions of <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1961Mashaf">Maṣḥafa saʿātāt</ref>,
              it is one of a few sǝbḥata fǝqur-hymns dedicated to various saints.</p>
